<plot>Johnny Valiant, former WWE, star is unsure what's coming next in life. The one thing he does know is that a day job is not for him. Sky Hosoya hopes her never say die attitude will bring her out of the dominatrix wrestling scene and into the world of professional wrestling stardom. Larry Degaris, professor by day, ring villain by night, explains the draw of the theater of the absurd that is wrestling. Jimmy Valiant is ready to call it quits after forty years in the ring and on the road.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?538822</url></doc>
